title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Part 1A
description:
OK gang, the 2nd part of the letter A.  Most torrent sites do not like torrents with thousands of files, and because each file is in fact 2 files, one MP3 and one CDG it is a problem, for uploading 600 songs is in fact 1200 files.

Part one track listing is enclosed as a text file suitable for import into the speadsheet of your choice for printing Karaoke books.

I don't want to ZIP or RAR them as that causes some users problems as well, so I will split the entire collection into 1GB or so chunks and get it out that way.

CDG+MP3 Karaoke correctly file named and tagged for playback from a Laptop.  Now features multiple choice for Karaoke Label on the more popular tracks.  Enjoy.

Rigmar Radio - Seeding to the World since 2004.  

OH AND a big THANKS TO USER ROFFE who cross posted my seeds over here when I could not post
